TowerInfoFragment.loadThemedBackground() does, it under the scenes

message:
Fix NPE bug

Steps: open app, place a tower, open its info fragment, open menu,
  open settings, change theme. Then TowerInfoFragment used getView()
  at onCreateView(), which rendered a null.

This bug wasn't reachable before I added the option to set a transparent
background for tower info fragment.
